  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="authorize-google" data-step-uuid="6B02D55F-A47C-409D-8708-D5786762AFF4">
    <h3 id="authorize-google" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Sign in to Google</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/935/416/original/6540db65-d2d2-42ae-a5aa-d23c2bb8dfcd.png" srcset="" alt="Sign in to Google" height="374" width="759">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_08EFACE7-BC98-4CE6-814E-42820AAE24AA" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If you have not previously authorized Google Drive access in Canvas, you may be prompted to sign in. Click the <strong>Sign in</strong> button.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/935/668/original/daf0bae6-793d-4173-a565-8f2afc764c8c.png" srcset="" alt="Select Google Account" height="538" width="484">
