    <p>Select your Google account.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="add_details" data-step-uuid="6A18BE85-85B8-42D0-AC29-92A4C9C83EE4">
    <h2 id="add_details" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Add Details</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/935/420/original/2d829fdc-de4e-4f0b-9231-de7808e007fb.png" srcset="" alt="Add Details" height="258" width="770">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_9451D0CB-39CC-441E-9DDB-81D5A6EF09CC" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To add a title for the collaboration, enter a title in the <strong>Title</strong> field [1].</p>
<p>In the <strong>File type</strong> drop-down menu, select the type of collaboration you want to create [2]. You can create docs, slides, sheets, forms, drawings, or sites.</p>
<p>To add a description for the collaboration, enter text in the <strong>Description </strong>field [3]. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="add_people" data-step-uuid="C2C04791-37EA-41F2-9C25-023CB9AADBF2">
    <h2 id="add_people" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Invite Collaborators</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/935/422/original/5dc8eeb0-f36f-41d3-80ed-6c5c2a10642f.png" srcset="" alt="Invite Collaborators" height="383" width="777">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_A04B747F-96BC-45F9-A16B-86FE31DAFDB0" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the checkbox next to the name of a user you want to add to the collaboration [1]. To select or deselect all users, click the <strong>Collaborators Selected</strong> checkbox [2].</p>
<p>Add as many users as necessary. </p>
<p><strong>Note: </strong>Collaborators must have a Google account and will need to authorize Canvas before they can view the collaboration.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

